sentences.english: Plutarch also recorded a number of physical characteristics about the pneuma.
sentences.chinese: 普魯塔克還記錄了靈氣的一些物理性質。

sentences.english: Would that then make consciousness a physical property?
sentences.chinese: 到那時是否意識會具有物理性質呢？

sentences.english: Because its unique photophysical property, and arise our interest to this research.
sentences.chinese: 因爲其特殊的光物理性質，引起我們對它研究的興趣。

sentences.english: And we are studying the properties of small, hot things.
sentences.chinese: 我們現在正是在研究小且熱的東西所具有的物理性質。

sentences.english: Furthermore, the degreasing ability of the HFEs was tested.
sentences.chinese: 測定了三種氟醚的物理性質及其去油能力。

sentences.english: Thermal conductivity is one of the most important parameters of thermophysical properties of materials.
sentences.chinese: 導熱係數是材料熱物理性質的重要參數之一。

sentences.english: The Pacific Rower makes ingenious use of the unique physical properties of water.
sentences.chinese: 太平洋賽艇使得巧妙利用獨特的物理性質的水。

sentences.english: Physical and rheological properties of extrudates were finally improved effectivly.
sentences.chinese: 所得擠出物的物理性質及其流變特性均有明顯改善。

sentences.english: The photophysical properties of the dyes in different solvents and solid matrices are researched.
sentences.chinese: 研究了它們在溶液和固體基質中的光物理性質。

sentences.english: This high-gloss, medium-impact grade offers a good balance of physical properties.
sentences.chinese: 這種高光澤，中衝級物理性質提供了很好的平衡。

sentences.english: In addition, the research advance on the physical character of foxtail millet is introduced.
sentences.chinese: 同時，對小米物理性質方面的研究進展也做了介紹。
